Reduces the loyalty penalty from additional cities for all (including modded*) factions.

By default, each additionally founded city will give -6 Loyalty to other cities. This reduces that penalty.

I saw a lot of versions of this concept, where the implementation only affected nonmodded factions. If someone already did this implementation, let me know so I can remove this; I might've missed it amidst the sea of mods.

